                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "As a self-proclaimed \"adventurer\" and newspaper celebrity, Ms. Hermosa knows a thing or two about drawing the spotlight onto herself, and the same goes when she's dueling at the card table. When building her favorite decks, her goal is clear: to \"create the most impressive visual effects\"!",
