                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: After a pneuma-ousia annihilation reaction occurs on an opponent's character, you gain 2 Omni Dice.",
